Package: EPhysMEA
Type: Package
Title: Analysis Tools for Multichannel Electrophysiology
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Moritz", "Lindner", email = "moritz@lindnerlab.de", role =
    c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Companion analysis package for 'EPhysData' providing binning and
    trial aggregation, tuning and receptive-field analysis, Naka-Rushton
    fitting, spike-train irregularity metrics, and ggplot2-based visualisation
    for 'EPhysEvents' and 'EPhysContinuous' objects.
